17
00:01:06,923 --> 00:01:09,771
1. Cache-Aside (Lazy Loading).

18
00:01:09,771 --> 00:01:13,389
The most common pattern - application manages the cache.

19
00:01:13,389 --> 00:01:14,615
2. Write-Through.

20
00:01:14,615 --> 00:01:18,461
Data is written to cache and database simultaneously.

21
00:01:18,461 --> 00:01:21,141
3. Write-Behind (Write-Back).

22
00:01:21,141 --> 00:01:25,480
Writes are batched and asynchronously persisted to the database.

23
